                     <interp inst="t18240715-18-off95" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240715-18-off95" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the 29th of June, one hundred bricks, value 3 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240715-18-victim244" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Wetherell
                  <interp inst="t18240715-18-victim244" type="surname" value="Wetherell"></interp>
